                  "revisionId": 2729781,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The speed at which Resonator moves to the selected location is affected by Ability Strength . Thus, this means that with a negative Ability Strength, the Resonator can move slower than normal. This can be useful for \"herding\" groups of enemies to a specific location without moving too fast and getting Resonator out of attraction range."
